data.name: labelInstructions.Text
data.value: Welcome To HackMan! In this game you will try to be the best hacker in the world! Try to learn a lot to get 100% of possibility of successful hacking and get intelligence to win with other hackers! Enlarge your computer kingdom by buying computers, hiring workers and constructing things. Be careful and don't get 4 stars and pay your bills for energy or you will lose. Have Fun!
